title: SME30 turntable samples, audiophile vinyl rip FLAC metadata
description:
Various LP tracks transcribed using the top of the line SME30 turntable, the Graham 2.2 unipivot tonearm, a Jan Allearts cartridge, Cardas Golden Reference tonearm cable and a $15,000 custom built tube phono stage employing high quality components (Lundahl amorphous core step up transformer, Cardas signal caps, oil filled power supply caps, tantalum resistors, NOS 6SN7 tubes, an 850 VA power transformer etc). 

Artists include Chris Isaak, Joni Mitchell, David Blue, John Lee Hooker, Rickie Lee Jones, Dave Brubeck, Albert King with Stevie Ray Vaughn, Louis Armstrong and a few more
